            <category>
                <![CDATA[rockstar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Rockstar Games]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209106</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Rockstar Games 的《GTA 6》近期推出了其预告片，立刻在全球引起轰动。这部预告片在首次 24 小时内就在 YouTube 上吸引了超过 9000 万次的观看，创下了惊人的纪录。根据健力士世界纪录的官方认证，《GTA 6》的预告片成功打破了三项纪录。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209109 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-1.26.04-PM-694x478.png" alt="" width="694" height="478" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-1.26.04-PM-694x478.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-1.26.04-PM-768x529.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-1.26.04-PM.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《GTA 6》破 3 项 YouTube 数据，24 小时内 YouTube 上总观看次数达 90,421,491</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">首先，《GTA 6》预告片以其 90,421,491 次的观看量，成为了 YouTube 上 24 小时内观看次数最多的电玩游戏影片。其次，该影片在同一时间段内获得了 890 万次的赞好，这使它成为了 YouTube 上 24 小时内获得赞好次数最多的电玩游戏影片。最后，除了音乐类型的影片，《GTA 6》的预告片还成为了 YouTube 上 24 小时内观看次数最多的影片，显示出其在游戏界的重大影响力。这些成就反映了玩家对《GTA 6》的高度期待，以及游戏在全球的广泛受欢迎程度。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《GTA 6》预告片在截稿时的浏览次数已超过 1 亿 1 千万。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_90307"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QdBZY2fkU-0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2023/12/grand-theft-auto-vi-first-look-becomes-most-viewed-videogame-trailer-in-24-hours-762030">Guinness World Record</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

